videos.description: President Barack Obama shakes fans hands before North Carolina and Duke take the court.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (President Obama greets fans at UNC-Duke game) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: President Obama greets fans at UNC-Duke game

videos.description: Zion Williamson cuts so hard his shoe falls apart, which causes him to fall down and lose the ball for a UNC layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion in pain after shoe comes apart) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: Zion in pain after shoe comes apart

videos.description: Tre Jones picks Coby White's pocket, but White tracks back and blocks his shot out of bounds.
videos.headline: White swats Jones' shot away

videos.description: Cameron Johnson beats RJ Barrett to the hoop, and Johnson flushes it home with two hands.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson slips through for easy dunk) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: Johnson slips through for easy dunk

videos.description: Javin DeLaurier throws down two back-to-back quick jams for the Blue Devils.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (DeLaurier dunks it twice in succession) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: DeLaurier dunks it twice in succession

videos.description: Seventh Woods tosses the ball up to an unmarked Garrison Brooks for the simple alley-oop connection.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Woods lobs it up to Brooks for alley-oop slam) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: Woods lobs it up to Brooks for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Duke and UNC trade ugly plays, but North Carolina is able to increase its lead to 10 after Garrison Brooks' dunk before the buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UNC closes out 1st half with a transition dunk) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: UNC closes out 1st half with a transition dunk

videos.description: Luke Maye advances the ball forward to Cameron Johnson, who drops it off to Coby White for the transition layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UNC's quick pace leads to White's lay-in) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: UNC's quick pace leads to White's lay-in

videos.description: Zion Williamson leaves the game with a knee injury after his shoe comes apart 33 seconds in.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion exits game after shoe falls apart, UNC leads at the half ) 2019/2/20 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: UNC builds halftime lead after Zion exits

videos.description: Seventh Woods meets minimal resistance, as he darts through the lane and lays the ball in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Woods strolls through for finger roll) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: Woods strolls through for finger roll

videos.description: Duke leaves Garrison Brooks unmanned, and Brandon Robinson tosses it up so Brooks can score the alley-oop layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Robinson lofts it up for Brooks' layup) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: Robinson lofts it up for Brooks' layup

videos.description: Cameron Johnson drives in and scores the layup off glass to increase UNC's lead on Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson's and-1 layup all but finishes off Duke) 2019/02/20

videos.headline: Johnson's and-1 layup all but finishes off Duke

videos.description: Zion Williamson suffers an injury 33 seconds into the game, and Cameron Johnson and Luke Maye combine for 56 points in UNC's big win over Duke.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Johnson, Maye take control after Zion’s injury) 2019/02/20 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Johnson, Maye take control after Zion's injury

videos.description: Mike Krzyzewski doesn't know the timetable after Zion Williamson's knee injury and laments losing another big player early in a Duke loss.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Coach K: Zion has a ‘mild knee sprain’) 2019/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coach K: Zion has a 'mild knee sprain'

videos.description: Jay Bilas talks about the impact Zion Williamsons' injury will have on Duke's scoring, as they struggled to put up points vs. UNC.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Where is Duke going to get scoring without Zion?) 2019/02/20 SC

videos.headline: Where is Duke going to get scoring without Zion?

videos.description: RJ Barrett addresses the injury to Zion Williamson, playing without him and is hopeful Zion is back for the next game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Barrett: Playing without Zion was tough) 2019/2/20

videos.headline: Barrett: Playing without Zion was tough
